[center][size=6][b][u]Compatibility & Troubleshooting[/u][/b][/size][/center][center][size=3]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/E5wWmag.png[/img]

As of [b]MOMI[/b] v0.7 and [b]Aurie[/b] 2.0, [b]YYTK[/b] mods are [u]no longer limited[/u] to the [b]Windows[/b] platform and [u]should work on Steam Deck and Linux[/u]. Additionally, any new installations of [b]YYTK[/b] mods using [b]MOMI[/b] v0.7+ will use [b]Aurie[/b] 2.0 to [u]patch the game directly[/u], eliminating the issues experienced in the past with false positive anti-virus reports due to mod DLL injection.[/size][/center]

[center][size=3]Given the amount of custom code this mod introduces, I have [u]no expectation[/u] of [b]WeMod[/b] or other tools being compatible. Feel free to report if they do or don't work, but I will not be able to help fix any compatibility issues.[/size][/center]


